# Functions
- when we want to use a block of code multiple times we use functions.
- # Function syntax:
  function_name(){
   ...
   ...
  }
- eg.
  #!/bin/bash
  function hello(){
   echo "Hello"
  }
  hello --> This will print Hello
- example of function with arguments:
  #!/bin/bash
  function hello(){
   echo "Hello $1"
  }
  hello "John" --> This will print Hello John